Package: SingleCellTools
Title: Wrapper and analysis functions for single cell data
Version: 2.5
Authors@R:
    person("K. Garrett", "Evensen", , "kgsevensen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6720-2526"))
Description: Opinionated wrappers over Seurat, Signac, and downstream analysis packages for
    scRNA-seq and spatial (Visium, Xenium, Parse Bio) workflows. Covers object construction,
    QC reporting and filtering, integration, marker-based and reference-based annotation,
    pseudobulk differential expression, composition testing, ligand-receptor inference,
    trajectory / pseudotime, spatial edge / hole / niche detection, and AnnData
    interoperability.
